        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <p class="font-label text-primary font-bold text-sm mb-2">ENTRY-LEVEL AUTOMATION</p>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm">250 GSM B-flute | Die-cut | ±3mm tolerance</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-label text-primary font-bold text-sm mb-2">MID-VOLUME CONVEYOR</p>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm">275 GSM B-flute | Die-cut | Label zone marked</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-label text-primary font-bold text-sm mb-2">AS/RS / ROBOT ARM</p>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm">300+ GSM BC-flute | Die-cut | Flap score</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-label text-primary font-bold text-sm mb-2">HIGH-THROUGHPUT 3PL</p>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm">Custom spec | ISO 2206 tolerance | Batch QC</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Warehouse Operations FAQs</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg p-4">
            <summary class="font-label font-bold text-on-surface cursor-pointer">How do I audit my current cartons for automation readiness?</summary>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Measure 20 random cartons; check dimensional variance, GSM, flute direction, and label zone consistency. Share findings with our team — we'll suggest upgrades.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg p-4">
            <summary class="font-label font-bold text-on-surface cursor-pointer">What's the price premium for automation-grade cartons?</summary>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Typically 8–12% above standard. The ROI is rapid: reducing line jams and mis-sorts saves far more than the per-carton premium.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg p-4">
            <summary class="font-label font-bold text-on-surface cursor-pointer">Can Quinocycle supply QR-coded cartons for traceability?</summary>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Yes. Pre-printed serialised QR codes and serial numbers are available for WMS traceability. Minimum order 2,000 cartons.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg p-4">
            <summary class="font-label font-bold text-on-surface cursor-pointer">What about mixed SKU dim requirements?</summary>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Most automated facilities allow 3–5 carton sizes within spec. Standardise on the smallest workable range to simplify your pick-and-pack flow.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg p-4">
            <summary class="font-label font-bold text-on-surface cursor-pointer">Lead time for first automation order?</summary>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">14 business days for die-cut automation-grade cartons with sample sign-off. Repeat orders ship within 7 days.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Upgrade Your Warehouse Carton Game</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Quinocycle's automation-grade cartons keep Malaysian warehouses running smoothly. Die-cut tolerance, consistent GSM, and engineered label zones — ready for your next automation rollout.</p>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface mb-6"><strong>Contact Quinocycle today:</strong></p>
        <ul class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>📞 <strong>Phone:</strong> +60 16 8916 381 / 03-8962 6381</li>
          <li>📧 <strong>Email:</strong> quinocycle@gmail.com</li>
          <li>📍 <strong>Address:</strong> No.13, Jalan Taming P/1, Taming Jaya, Balakong, Selangor 43300</li>
        </ul>
        <a href={WA_LINK} class="inline-block bg-primary text-on-primary font-label font-bold text-sm px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">💬 Chat on WhatsApp</a>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Conclusion: Packaging Is Part of the Automation Stack</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-4">Automated warehouses succeed or stall on the quality of the inputs they receive. Generic cartons cause jams. Automation-grade cartons run smooth lines at full throughput. The ROI on a spec upgrade is measured in weeks, not years.</p>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed">Quinocycle has supplied Selangor warehousing operations since 2010. Ready to scale your automation? Let's talk.</p>
